Author: NeuntyNeun
Text: I get you but I’m also running on some hard core double think like on the one hand I can see my ribs and the cave when I bend my knees and I get that objectively it’s pretty gross but at the same time I also know my calves and upper arms are huge. Basically I look half anorexic half fat and it’s just EUGH WHY GOD.   I see myself and think ‘damn I really am skinny’ then a whole 2 minutes later see myself again and I’m like ‘is this a reason to *starve for 204749192747292 years*

Author: coffinOfcans
Text: My brother said I look anorexic now. All I see is FATTTTTTTT in the mirror. I can’t look at my reflection at all. Kill me. Huge. I feel like he’s lying... do you feel the same?
